he wind, as well as the torque. This allows for considerable\npredictive power, and is an improvement over existing approximations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Jan 2008 20:57:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Jan 2008 01:09:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 18 Jan 2008 06:17:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
