e a $B_x-T$ phase diagram\ncompatible with the experiments in the small semi-classical $B_x$ regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Jan 2008 21:30:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-14"}
